text: Rockdale Ilinden Football Club (known as Rockdale City Suns Football Club from 1992 to 2020) is an Australian semi-professional soccer club based in Rockdale, a suburb of Sydney. It competes in the National Premier Leagues NSW (NPL NSW). It was founded by Macedonian Australians and has strong connections to Sydney's Macedonian community. Category:Soccer clubs in Sydney
title: Rockdale Ilinden FC
